node.text: On May the 4th 1970, the #KentState Massacre occurred and cannabis ended up as a scapegoat, which led to some pretty awful legislation that still exists today 😔 Full video can be found on @herb’s Facebook page! I’m there every Tuesday at 12p PST!

node.text:
I decided to interview my twin brother @cannabistim12! His second cannabis interview ever! 

We went down memory lane and talked about his business endeavors Legal dispensary, @goodkarmacannabisco + Hookah & Consumption Lounge @hubblybubblyokc + A Positive News Podcast @thepositivetruthpodcast + A Smoke Shop @trifectaokc 🔥Tim is killin it 👏🏽 #proudsister

node.text: Thank you @dontewest for sharing your story 🙏🏽 Today, we discussed his journey through the criminal justice system for a cannabis conviction that was levied against with practically no evidence and a false testimony. node.text:
🚨LEGALIZE IT EVERYWHERE🚨
America is making huge gains on the drug war, but did you know legalization in other parts of the world benefits us and the planet? 🌎Let’s help push India’s cannabis/medicinal herb reform efforts! 🇮🇳 Here’s how to do it:
✨First, follow @hempvati!
✨Second, go to the link in my bio! Under “Cannabis Reform,” you will find the submission link for opinions and suggestions on cannabis, psilocybin and other herbs to India’s government.
✨Share and tell a friend or family member to help, too!

I believe we can affect change globally! Will you help?

node.text:
CBD & Cannabis -- Can CBD really tame your cannabis high? We've all heard someone say if you're too high, take some CBD. But did you know research actually shows it can do the opposite, making you higher? It all comes down to the dosage, and obviously as with everything cannabis, the experience varies from person to person.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Scientists found that a high dose of CBD [400mg] was effective in curbing a THC high [8mg], but that participants actually had a stronger high at a lower dose of CBD [4mg].⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Can you relate to these findings? Let me know your experiences in the comments!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
📷: @lilxbun

node.text:
How many are you are familiar with decarboxylation?⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Decarboxylation is essentially the process that activates certain compounds in cannabis. For example, when you see a strain label high in THCA, it hasn't been decarboxylated into THC. In order for decarboxylation to occur, you need heat and time.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
With flower, drying and curing can cause partial decarboxylation, and when smoking or vaping it instantly happens with the high temperatures present - making other cannabinoids available through inhalation.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Have you ever attempted to decarboxylate cannabis at home - outside of smoking it?⁠⁠
⁠⁠
📷: @maryjenny.style

node.text:
ICYMI: Amazon announced its support in June for nationwide cannabis legalization, stating the company would also stop testing employees for cannabis use. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
This is a big deal, being that Amazon is the nation's second largest company it has the potential to make waves for federal legalization. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Some small business owners are worried about whether or not the retail giant will start delivering cannabis, and what it could mean for their sales. What are your thoughts? Sound off in the comments! 🔊⁠⁠
⁠⁠
📷: @londonroseruby

node.text: Sometimes you need that extra puff, puff, puff, puff, pass.. 💨 What are your favorite strains for stress relief?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Tammy💗The Cannabis Cutie, MBA in Los Angeles, California with @highbuhd.

node.text:
It's terpene time! Today I'm talking Pinene, the most common terpene in the natural world. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Much like its name would suggest, pinene smells and tastes like pine needles. Outside of cannabis, it can be found in orange peels, turpentine, rosemary, dill, basil, and parsley.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
While a lot of pinene's effects depend on the specific strain, it has been known to be anti-inflammatory, anti-anxiety, and good for pain relief.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Some high-pinene strains include Blue Dream, Grape Ape, Cannatonic, and Harlequin.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Have a terpene you want to know more about? Let me know in the comments! ↓ ↓ ↓⁠⁠
⁠⁠
📷: @highbuhd
